{"tid":1821191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【係愛呀哈利！】「哈利波特」自爆被當乞兒 獲陌生人送暖畀5蚊","createTime":"2020-01-12T05:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T08:28:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b986ac0c387435e250331bc0f8e4a13a4d25ac3","tid":1821191,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"「哈利波特」丹尼爾拉德克里夫（ Daniel Radcliffe）現時已經30歲，不再是當年可愛的四眼仔，雖然長大後樣貌已大為不同，但他近日竟然自爆不被認得之餘，更被陌生人當乞兒！<br />\n他近日上名嘴Graham Norton 節目接受訪問，自爆曾於紐約被當乞兒。當時他正在店外等女朋友，並跪下與狗狗一起取暖。之後有一名好心的陌生人上前，給了他5蚊美金（約港幣39元），丹尼爾表示：「那個男人看着我微笑，走過我5步之後，又再重新出現，給了我一張5蚊紙幣，並說：『幫你自己買杯咖啡吧，老友。』」令丹尼爾哭笑不得：「好明顯，我要剃鬚剃得頻密點了！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200112/large/1578806142_240a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200112%2Flarge%2F1578806142_240a.jpg&h=335b2883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200112/large/1578806143_76b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200112%2Flarge%2F1578806143_76b5.jpg&h=16a719b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60476830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60476830&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=edadd91b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60476830&h=591de22b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20200112/60476830</a>"},{"pid":"d3f5333826ac7f9d4fe5c4ba6975e6f6e2b6bc4f","tid":1821191,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e46d4d912c5e1ab5097f84d550ea09bc99ec5720",